# Client Dashboard Routing — Air Fryer Probe

This repo is an operational knowledge base, not the public website. **`website.brand_source: ops_local`**

Before any task, read `AGENTS.md`, `company/facts.yaml`, and `company/content-policy.md`.

## Brand routing

| Source | Location |
|--------|----------|
| Design system | `company/brand/design.md` |
| Voice | `company/brand/voice.md` |
| Brand facts (price, specs) | `company/brand-facts.yaml` |
| Assets | `company/brand/assets/` · `social/assets-manifest.md` |
| Resolve path | `./scripts/resolve-website-asset.sh logos/artboard-2.svg` |

## Hard rules

- **Logo:** SVG from `company/brand/assets/logos/` — never retype "AIR FRYER"
- **Temps:** `company/temperature-guide.md` — chicken = **74°C**, no carry-over offsets
- **Bundle:** Market 3-in-1 (probe + guide + hook); mini screwdriver in-the-box only
- **Voice:** No *revolutionary* or *game-changing* in brand copy
- **Follower counts:** Never cite in new copy

## Reference only

`reference/site-content/` · `reference/facebook-posts/` — rewrite to canonical before publishing.

Client dashboard: `content/` → `dashboard/` build → Netlify password protection.
